Name:                print-debugger
Version:             1.1.7
Stability:           beta
Description:         Print debugging with stack trace for Haskell (formatted for ease 	                   of use). See screenshot: http://i.imgur.com/KCXYHNk.png
Synopsis:            Debug print formatting library.
License:             PublicDomain
License-file:        LICENSE
Extra-source-files:  README
Author:              John-Michael Reed
Maintainer:          johnmichaelreedfas@gmail.com
Homepage:	     https://github.com/JohnReedLOL/HaskellPrintDebugger
Category:            Debug
Build-type:          Simple
Cabal-Version:       >= 1.10
Tested-with:         GHC==7.10.3
Bug-reports:         https://github.com/JohnReedLOL/HaskellPrintDebugger/issues

Source-repository head
  type:              git
  location:          https://github.com/JohnReedLOL/HaskellPrintDebugger

Library
  ghc-options:       -Wall
  build-depends:     base <4.10, split
  exposed-modules:   Debug.Print.StackTraceDebug
  default-language:  Haskell2010
  Hs-source-dirs:    src
